writeArray

Line[] writeArray
writeArray : in reader's eyes, reader get data from data source and write data to this line array. readArray : in writer's eyes, writer put data to data destination from this line array. Because of this is doubleQueue mechanism, the two line will exchange when time is suitable.

Line[] readArray
writeArray : in reader's eyes, reader get data from data source and write data to this line array. readArray : in writer's eyes, writer put data to data destination from this line array. Because of this is doubleQueue mechanism, the two line will exchange when time is suitable.
